  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2D idle game about farming various crops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818590/extras/bb16fb465de795c787f95fc40e921622.poster.avif?t=1764181586\" width=1170 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818590/extras/bb16fb465de795c787f95fc40e921622.webm?t=1764181586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818590/extras/bb16fb465de795c787f95fc40e921622.mp4?t=1764181586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use crops to <strong>produce new materials</strong>, buy <strong>upgrades</strong> and sell them for <strong>profit</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They are used in dozens of <strong>recipes</strong> to gain even better <strong>buffs</strong> for your ranch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818590/extras/7b1eb6b6ef1f8429a0255fe6d11443b3.poster.avif?t=1764181586\" width=1170 height=642 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818590/extras/7b1eb6b6ef1f8429a0255fe6d11443b3.webm?t=1764181586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scale to crazy numbers and make bank. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818590/extras/40e6ccb1ae4cabf15d6e62945a8f0a7e.poster.avif?t=1764181586\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://sha